                            <comment id="13621432" author="mbertozzi" created="Wed, 3 Apr 2013 22:32:40 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Should the numeric value for the above two enum&apos;s be increased after the movement ?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It doesn&apos;t really matter, the numeric value is never used...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RegionTransitionData.write() uses eventType.ordinal() that is the index in the enum and not the value specified in the enum definition.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but I like the... &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
